Oblivious to the violation, Fallon Fraker continues paying as the peeping tom calmly sidles out of the convenience store towards his getaway motorcycle parked in the forecourt.

A manhunt has now been launched after 
CCTV caught the voyeur taking the picture on his mobile phone at a 
Raceway petrol station in League City, Texas.

